                <li>Death scenes</li>
                <li>Jumpscare</li>
              </ul>
              <pre>You wake up to a loud crash downstairs. 
</pre>
              <blockquote>Sounds like something broke. If you could blame this on a pet or a sibling, that would be great and you could go right back to sleep.&nbsp; &nbsp; <br>&nbsp; <br>Unfortunately, you live entirely alone. You have no choice but to check it out.</blockquote>
              <p>A short horror VN that's more satirical than scary. Your goal is to survive an encounter with a home intruder with characteristics beyond your comprehension. <br></p>
              <p>It's 15-20 minutes of gameplay (more or less to get all <strong>6 endings</strong>) and the walkthrough can be found in the development log at the bottom of the page, if you want to avoid the jumpscare.</p>
              <p>This is my first game project I made in a week, so I don't plan to update it with anything substantial. Gavril is a major character from my story BUBO, which I'm planning to make more games for. You can find out more on my socials: <a href="https://twitter.com/Partulla_" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">Twitter</a> / <a href="https://www.instagram.com/partuulla/" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">Instagram</a> / <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCZTMHEq8z9K0qL6v4YlXt1A" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">YT</a><br></p>
